    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S) In nomine domini dei eterni, anno hab (sic) incarnatione eius millesimo
                        centesimo LXIII, sesta kal. decembris, inditione duodecima. Manifesti sumus
                        nos <persName ref="#people/3235">Bonifatius</persName> et <persName
                            ref="#people/3234">Buiamonte</persName> germani filii quondam <persName
                            ref="#people/3227">Uguicioni</persName>
                        <persName ref="#people/3228">Bonifatii</persName> et uxoris eius <persName
                            ref="#people/3237">Cangniola</persName> filia <persName><name
                                ref="Widuccius">Guiduci</name></persName> et <persName
                            ref="#people/3236">Giemma</persName> filia <persName><name
                                ref="Aldebrandus">Aldobrandi</name></persName>, anbo iste
                        interrogate sunt a <persName key="#Judge"><name ref="Piculus"
                            >Picculo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudice</rs>, (…) quia per hanc cartulam venditionis
                        vindimus et tradimus<orgName key="#Hospitals" ref="#juridical_persons/3206">
                            <rs key="#Hospitals">iosspitale</rs>
                            <placeName ref="#places/3207" key="#Hospitals"
                            >Altipasti</placeName></orgName> venerabili loco in manum
                                <persName><name ref="Montanus">Montanini</name></persName> rectori
                        osspitalis idem una petia de terra que est posita in loco qui vocatur Prata
                        in <rs key="#Seigneurial_district">curte</rs> de <placeName
                            ref="#places/3210" key="#Roads #Seigneurial_district">Puteo</placeName>.
                        Tamen decernimus terram petia ipsa cuide una parte est fini terre del
                                <persName><name ref="Vecchio">Vecchio</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Alcheruolus">Alchiruoli</name></persName>. De
                        secunda parte est fini terre <persName><name ref="Bonardus"
                            >Bonardi</name></persName>. De tertia parte est fini terre <persName
                            ref="#people/3217">Adimari</persName> et <persName><name
                                ref="Widaloctus">Guidalocti</name></persName>. De quarta parte est
                        fini terra <rs key="#Roads">via pubblica</rs> currit. Ideo predicta petia
                        terra novem staiora ad iusta pertica misurata, unum panorum et medium mino
                        (…) vendimus et tradimus (…). Pro ipsa venditione nostram (sic) recepimus
                        nos (…) inter argentum et alias mobilias prova valiente libre novem et sol.
                        XII de bonis denaris de Lucca et di Pisa. (…). <foreign>Pena</foreign>:
                        dupplum. (…) Actum <placeName ref="#places/3227">Gangalandi</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Comitatus">comitatu</rs>
                        <geogName key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/83">florentino</geogName>. Signum
                        manum supradictorum iugalium (…). Signa manuum <persName><name ref="Salomon"
                                >Salamoni</name></persName> filius <persName><name
                                ref="Wido/Mariolus">Guidi Mariole</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Wido">Guidocti</name></persName> filius
                                <persName><name ref="Tancredus">Tancridi</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Rodelandus Moricti">Orlandini
                            Moricti</name></persName> et <persName><name ref="Zoppus Moricti">Zoppi
                                Moricti</name></persName> et <persName><name ref="Martinus de Puteo"
                                >Martinelli</name> de Puteo</persName>, qui ibidem fuerunt rogati
                        testes. (S) Ego Picculus notarius post tradita dicta complevi.
                                <persName><name ref="Falco">Falco</name></persName> rogavi sta (sic)
                        cartula et recepi in sua manum a vice osspitium Altipasti. </ab>
                </div>
